text1: And he sent Eliakim , who was over the household , and Shebna the scribe , and the elders of the priests , covered with sackcloth , unto Isaiah the prophet the son of Amoz .
text2: And he sent Eliakim , who was over the house , and Shebna the scribe , and the chief priests , dressed in haircloth , to Isaiah the prophet , the son of Amoz .

text1: The word of the Lord which came to Joel , the son of Pethuel .
text2: The word of the Lord that came to Joel the son of Phatuel .

text1: having become by so much better than the angels , as he hath inherited a more excellent name than they .
text2: taking a place by so much better than the angels , as he inherits a name more excellent than they .

text1: When therefore he was gone out , Jesus saith , Now is the Son of man glorified , and God is glorified in him ;
text2: When therefore he was gone out Jesus says , Now is the Son of man glorified , and God is glorified in him .
